{"tid":614124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佐敦軒達臣遭球迷狂噓：不配當隊長！","createTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T12:25:23.000Z","uid":147522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"627aa7c4a2d8c0915f9f2f5a5c7aff40e2e35110","tid":614124,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"在昨晚進行的英超聯賽中，雖然利物浦2-1戰勝水晶宮，但紅軍隊長軒達臣的表現讓球迷們很不滿。<br />\n　　12分鐘水晶宮獲得12碼，而這個12碼來自於賓迪基頭槌傳給沙夏後創造的機會，當時軒達臣站在賓迪基身旁，幾乎沒有干擾對方的爭頂。對此利物浦球迷們紛紛在社交媒體上批評稱，「隊長讓賓迪基太輕易爭到頭槌」、「軒達臣表現真的非常糟糕，讓賓迪基輕鬆爭頂。」<br />\n　　還有一些紅軍球迷甚至喊出讓軒達臣走人的口號，「我為自己說利物浦今天不能贏波道歉，但我不會為自己說讓軒達臣離開我的球會而道歉！」「我之前說過，現在再說一遍&hellip;&hellip;軒達臣簡直就是在搶劫。」「我無法接受軒達臣繼續為利物浦效力。」「談到軒達臣是利物浦的隊長真的讓我很尷尬。」<br />\n　　不過利物浦教練高普似乎依然完全信任軒達臣，之前高普還曾表示，「軒達臣是個令人不可思議的隊長，利物浦需要這類球員，他們是領導者。」"},{"pid":"d290bd73245a4c88c02c9dcff5bdaf95b1be44a7","tid":614124,"uid":27416,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"軒仔撈到英利雙料隊長真係好勵志"},{"pid":"9aee45a59453f0d5e2a35ea215c259d69ad6046b","tid":614124,"uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/171048_0b56566c1bab0c8ac400ad0a09911a1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F171048_0b56566c1bab0c8ac400ad0a09911a1b.jpg&h=befda2dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e16964424e02140ecf8864b885fd439bc7779c39","tid":614124,"uid":64225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d290bd73245a4c88c02c9dcff5bdaf95b1be44a7","tid":614124,"uid":27416,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"軒仔撈到英利雙料隊長真係好勵志"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:12:33.000Z","msg":"真係唔知行咩運"},{"pid":"c4318c5b271dd22925b5494e8f54f7ced6720229","tid":614124,"uid":5549,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:08:03.000Z","msg":"唔識波先話神軒唔勁，神軒，卡域克，殺卡，呢三個要識波先知係英超史上最強deep lying midfielder<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7900025d988ba490c72e42b3205a884265fd03","tid":614124,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"猁不配擁有神軒"},{"pid":"5f0e3766ffac403dfbb178d831df74fb64ddbbdb","tid":614124,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"本身球12碼唔係個龍on99衝出黎撞鳩人都唔會有架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d4a82a48f07daf400797d481ce27aeca4b7fa9","tid":614124,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aee45a59453f0d5e2a35ea215c259d69ad6046b","tid":614124,"uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/171048_0b56566c1bab0c8ac400ad0a09911a1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F171048_0b56566c1bab0c8ac400ad0a09911a1b.jpg&h=befda2dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"朗隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5400db8548399bb769755650e74a84bd121b91","tid":614124,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"周身刀，無張利"},{"pid":"0442746005eb6ae08e8f1848d8b09ffd6e27ca00","tid":614124,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"死利狗食屎大？"},{"pid":"f9a0870aed6b38ba55eb51d097cfe319872a6c65","tid":614124,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d4a82a48f07daf400797d481ce27aeca4b7fa9","tid":614124,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aee45a59453f0d5e2a35ea215c259d69ad6046b","tid":614124,"uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/171048_0b56566c